<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GetyourHR</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">


</head>

<body>
    <div class="categoryForm">
        <nav>
            <div class="logoImg">
                <img src="/assets/yourHR-type-logo.png" alt="">
            </div>
        </nav>

        <div class="uploadOptions">
            <div class="category candidate">
                <h2>JOB SEEKER</h2>
                <div>

                    <!-- -----------------------------for job seeker------------------------------- -->
                    <div class="categoryDetails">
                        <div class="categoryImg">
                            <center>
                                <img src="/assets/candidate_Form.png" alt="candidate form image with a woman working">
                            </center>
                        </div>
                        <div class="categoryContent">
                            <p>Upload your resume and find jobs related to your skills and your resume.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="formDetails">
                            <p>Upload Resume</p>
                            <form action="/uploadResume" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                                <div class="dropBox">
                                    <span class="drop-zone__prompt">Attach file</span>
                                    <input type="file" name="resume" required class="drop-zone__input">
                                </div>
                                <br>
                                <button type="submit">Submit</button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                     <!-- ----------------------------- job seeker ends--------------------------------->
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="category referee">
                <h2>EMPLOYER</h2>
                <!-- ---------------------------------for referee------------------------------------------- -->
                <div class="categoryDetails">
                    <div class="refereeImg">
                        <center>
                            <img src="/assets/referee_Hiring.png" alt="employer form image with a man working">
                        </center>
                    </div>
                    <div class="categoryContent">
                        <p>Provide a link to your job and your credentials for job seekers to apply to the job.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="refereeForm">
                        <form action="/submitJobPost" method="POST">
                            <input type="url" placeholder="Link for the Job" name="jobLink" required style="margin-top: 20px;">
                            <br>
                            <input type="email" placeholder="Email Address" name="email" required style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 8px;">
                            <br>
                            <button type="submit">Find Now</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- --------------------------------- referee ends------------------------------------------- -->
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="aboutContainer">

        <div class="aboutInfoDiv">
            <div class="aboutInfo">
                <h2>About Our Company</h2>
                <div class="informationAbout">
                    <p>All companies provide referral bonuses to their employees, but a significant portion of them are unable to take advantage of this opportunity due to lack of their professional network to refer someone and therefore miss out on earning the bonus.<br><br>
                        At Get your HR, we believe that referrals are the future of hiring. That's why we've built a platform that connects employees, job seekers, and companies, making it easier and faster to find the perfect fit.</p>
                </div>
                <br>
                <div class="learnMoreBtn">
                    <button type="submit">Learn More</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="aboutImgDiv">
            <img src="/assets/aboutImg.png" alt="people discussing">
        </div>

    </div>


    <div class="howItWorks">
        <div class="howIWpara">
            <center>
            <h2>How It Works?</h2>
            <p>Get your HR ensure that no money is left on the table. In just 4 steps, we let employee tap into the referral bonus, Get job seeker an offer and help companies find the right candidate faster.</p>
            </center>
        </div>

        <div class="howIWsteps">
            <div class="HIWStepsImg">
                <img src="/assets/howItWorksImg.png" alt="person typing on laptop">
            </div>
            <div class="HIWSteps">
                <div class="stepGrp">
                    <div class="stepHeading">
                        <p><span class="blueColorStep">STEP 1</span>-EMPLOYEE</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stepContent">
                        <p>Uploads the links to open positions in their company that they can refer to.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="stepGrp">
                    <div class="stepHeading">
                        <p><span class="blueColorStep">STEP 2</span>-JOB SEEKERS</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stepContent">
                        <p>Uploads their resumes.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="stepGrp">
                    <div class="stepHeading">
                        <p><span class="blueColorStep">STEP 3</span>-YourHR</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stepContent">
                        <p>Find the best match and suggest profiles to Employees.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="stepGrp">
                    <div class="stepHeading">
                        <p><span class="blueColorStep">STEP 4</span>-EMPLOYEES + JOB&nbsp;SEEKERS + YourHR</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stepContent">
                        <p>Employees engage with the job seekers and refer them for the job.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="winTag">
            <center>
            <p>It is a <span class="winGreen">WIN WIN WIN!</span> Situation for Everyone</p>
            </center>
        </div>
    </div>


    <script src="/index.js"></script>
</body>

</html>